xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:778:\"<p>We are pleased to announce an updated version of WP-Optimize 2.2.11 for both free and paid versions.</p>\n<p>We recommend the update for all WP-Optimize users.</p>\n<p>The full changelog is as follows;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>FIX</strong>: A regression in the &#8220;identify table by owner&#8221; feature caused optimizing to silently fail on some tables</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Added ability to exclude lazy load images by class&#8220;`</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-11-now-released/\">WP-Optimize 2.2.11 now released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-11-now-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-optimize-2-2-11-now-released/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"UpdraftPlus 1.16.4 / 2.16.4 now released\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/UpdraftPlus/~3/Mhvk-h1blac/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-1-16-4-2-16-4-now-released/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 17 Jan 2019 11:12:05 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"UpdraftPlus development news\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"updraft plus\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"UpdraftPlus development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"updraftplus premium\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://updraftplus.com/?p=338574\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:728:\"<p>We are pleased to announce that UpdraftPlus 1.16.4 (free version) and 2.16.4 (paid versions) have been released. The changes in this new release cover a number of fixes and tweaks for both versions. We recommend the update for all UpdraftPlus &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-1-16-4-2-16-4-now-released/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-1-16-4-2-16-4-now-released/\">UpdraftPlus 1.16.4 / 2.16.4 now released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2503:\"<p>We are pleased to announce that UpdraftPlus 1.16.4 (free version) and 2.16.4 (paid versions) have been released. The changes in this new release cover a number of fixes and tweaks for both versions. We recommend the update for all UpdraftPlus users.</p>\n<p>The full change-log is as follows;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>FIX</strong>: Regression: Properly mark backups picked up via &#8220;Rescan remote storage&#8221; as non-native (preventing unwelcome side-effects such as being pruned by another site)</li>\n<li><strong>FIX</strong>: Correctly update the OneDrive refresh token to prevent expiry</li>\n<li><strong>FIX</strong>: Again work around an issue with &#8216;SSH2 Server Host Key Algorithm Mismatch&#8217; occurring with the current phpseclib release by temporarily reverting to an earlier one as it still does not work on all installs</li>\n<li><strong>FIX</strong>: When restoring an incremental backup set via WP-CLI, the selected restore point was ignored</li>\n<li><strong>FIX</strong>: If the remote storage settings were for multiple instances of a single backend-type (e.g. two Dropbox accounts), and if the entire backup and send operation completed in a single PHP process, then the local copy of the files would not be deleted</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Show the error message if mbstring.func_overload is turned on in php.ini while creating migration key</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Added Azure China endpoint</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Resolve &#8220;dashicons&#8221; CSS conflict</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Add &#8216;blogmeta&#8217; to the list of core tables (in readiness for WP 5.1)</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Remove unnecessary deprecated (in PHP 7.3) parameter to define() in WebDAV HTTP library</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Prevent a potential PHP notice in UpdraftPlus Premium when installed without network access</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Enhance the updraftplus_exclude_file and updraftplus_exclude_directory filters to also pass the stored names</li>\n<li><strong>TWEAK</strong>: Add a new constant UPDRAFTPLUS_ZIP_BATCH_CEILING that can tweak internals of the zip backup engine&#8220;`</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-1-16-4-2-16-4-now-released/\">UpdraftPlus 1.16.4 / 2.16.4 now released</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-1-16-4-2-16-4-now-released/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"ht